  "description": "Fix Persistent Menu Expansion Issue\n\nResolve the issue where the menu remains constantly expanded instead of collapsing properly when expected.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify why the menu stays in an expanded state\n- Implement proper toggle functionality to allow menu expansion and collapse\n- Ensure menu state is controlled correctly (open/closed)\n- Verify click handlers and event listeners are working as intended\n- Check if menu state is being persisted incorrectly (localStorage, state management)\n- Test menu behavior across different screen sizes and devices\n- Ensure menu collapses when clicking outside the menu area (if applicable)\n- Verify no CSS or styling conflicts forcing the menu to appear expanded\n- Add proper default state (collapsed on page load unless intentionally expanded)",
